		 <a name="Rainbow_Six_Siege"> <h4> Rainbow Six Siege <h4/> </a> 
			<img src="../Images/R6S.jpg">
		
			<p> Rainbow Six Siege is a 1st person shooting game that is developed by Ubisoft. <br> Rainbow Six Siege is played by 2.3 million players and has a competitive pro league.  
			<br> This game give you the opportunity to attack and defend different sites on several maps. It also offers you 40 unique operators which have different gadgets and weapons. <br> I like this game because:
			    
			</p>
			<ol>
			<li> It's extremely fun to play </li>
			<li> Realistic </li>
			<li> You have the ability to make and shape different starts </li>
			<li> You can go pro </li>
			<li> The mechanics in this game is extremely powerful </li>
			</ol>
			
			<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RPY3TQSolm4"> Trailer </a>
			
			<!-- I extremely love this game and have my own competitive team -->
			
