		 <a name="Yu_Gi_Oh"> <h4> Yu Gi Oh </h4> </a>
			<img src="../Images/Yu Gi Oh.jpg">
		
			<p> Yu Gi Oh is a card game buit based on the famous japanese anime by the producer Charles Murakami. <br> Yu Gi Oh is played across all platforms. <br> I like this game because:
			</p>
			<ol>
			<li> Gives you the opportunity to expreince 3D visuals of monsters </li>
			<li> You can customize your own deck </li>
			<li> Gives you the chance to collect cards </li>
			<li> You can play multiplier as well as stroy mode </li>
			</ol>
			
		<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nZnZOuvGQVU"> Trailer </a>
		
