		<a name="Command_&_Conquer:_Generals"> <h4> Command & Conquer: Generals </h4> </a> 
			<img src="../Images/Command & Conquer Generals.jpg">
		
			<p> Command & Conquer: Generals is a real-time strategy video game and the seventh installment in the Command & Conquer series. It was released for Microsoft Windows and Mac OS operating systems in 2003 and 2004 "wikipedia". <br> Unfortunately this game is only available on PC. <br> I like this game because:
			</p>
			<ol>
			<li> You can play multiplier as well as stroy mode </li>
			<li> The story mode is based on real life wars that has happened </li>
			<li> You have the ability to choose the army you want </li>
			<li> This game gives you the chance to customize and build your own base </li>
			</ol>
			
		<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PmaJL8U50Ik"> Trailer </a>
		
