		<a name="Counter-Strike:_Global_Offensive"> <h4> Counter-Strike: Global Offensive </h4> </a> 
			<img src="../Images/Counter-Strike Global Offensive.jpg">
		
			<p> Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (CS:GO) is a multiplayer first-person shooter video game developed by Hidden Path Entertainment and Valve Corporation "wikipedia". <br> Unfortunately this game is only available on PC and xbox 360. Hopefully developers make this game compatible for XBOX one and PS4 in the near future as it is extremely fun to play.
				<br> I like this game because:
			</p>
			<ol>
			<li> Multiplier is extremely fun to play </li>
			<li> I like this in particular because I grow up playing this game </li>
			<li> This game has a pro league scene </li>
			</ol>
			
