		<a name="007:_Quantum_of_Solace"> <h4> 007: Quantum of Solace </h4> </a> 
			<img src="../Images/007 Quantum of Solace.jpg">
		
			<p> 007: Quantum of Solace is a first-person shooter video game based on the films Casino Royale and Quantum of Solace. The game was released for Microsoft Windows, Nintendo DS, PlayStation 2, PlayStation 3, Wii and Xbox 360 "wikipedia".
				<br> This game was initially released in October 31, 2008. This game uses IW engine. 
				<br> I like this game because:
			</p>
			<ol>
			<li> Having an amazing story mode </li>
			<li> The movement mechanics are extremely good in my opinion </li>
			<li> I like this game in particular because of the shooting mechanics </li>
			</ol>
			
